<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <!-- home page -->
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Saberchat</title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.0/css/bootstrap.min.css"
          integrity="sha384-9aIt2nRpC12Uk9gS9baDl411NQApFmC26EwAOH8WgZl5MYYxFfc+NcPb1dKGj7Sk" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/main.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/home/index.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/components/background.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/components/navbar.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/components/header.css">
    <% if (currentUser) { %>
        <% if (currentUser.darkmode) { %>
            <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/Darkmode.css">
        <% } %>
    <% } %>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.min.js"
            integrity="sha256-9/aliU8dGd2tb6OSsuzixeV4y/faTqgFtohetphbbj0=" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/@popperjs/core@2" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.0/js/bootstrap.min.js"
            integrity="sha384-OgVRvuATP1z7JjHLkuOU7Xw704+h835Lr+6QL9UvYjZE3Ipu6Tp75j7Bh/kR0JKI"
            crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/dccc745c41.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="/javascript/nav/userForm.js"></script>
    <script src="/javascript/nav/navbar.js"></script>
    <script src="/javascript/home/index.js"></script>
</head>
<body class="mode">

<!-- insert navbar via ejs-->
<%- include('./partials/navbar') %>

<!-- Background image and text -->
<section id="background">
    <div class="container-fluid text-center background-inner-div">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-12 background-title">
                <h1 style="user-select: none; -moz-user-select: none;">Saberchat</h1>
                <p style="user-select: none; -moz-user-select: none;">Welcome to Saberchat, Alsion's very own
                    communication platform!</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Home Page content -->
<main id="main-container">
    <div class="container mt-5 mode">
        <!-- Block 1 -->
        <div class="row element" id="about">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <article class="text-block">
                    <div class="block-header green">
                        <h1 style="user-select: none; -moz-user-select: none;">About</h1>
                    </div>
                    <div class="block-content mode">
                        <p>Named after our school mascot, the sabercat, Saberchat is a platform that connects and
                            centralizes Alsion's various communication and notification platforms, streamlining
                            communication between students, faculty, parents and more.</p>
                        <p>Users can quickly access any important information from faculty, communicate with others,
                            order from the No Left Turn Caf√©, and access some of Alsion's unique projects.</p>
                        <p>Centralizing our school's content to an inclusive platform serves to improve our school's
                            identity as well as the relationships between students, parents, and faculty across the
                            community.</p>
                        <span id="developers"><span id="developers-heading">Developers: </span>Alexander Zhou, Kabir Samsi, Siddharth Chavan, Vibhav Darsha, Dmitry Pleshkov</span>
                    </div>
                </article>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 block">
                <img class="image-block" src="https://alsionschool.org/images/middle-school/MiddleSchoolMainPage.jpg"
                     alt="fancy pic">
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Block 2 -->
        <div class="row element" id="block-2">
            <div class="col-lg-6 order-lg-2">
                <article class="text-block">
                    <div class="block-header yellow">
                        <h1 style="user-select: none; -moz-user-select: none;">Services</h1>
                    </div>
                    <div class="block-content mode">
                        <ul>
                            <li><span class"feature-description" >Chat rooms</span> for students and teachers</li>
                            <li>An <span class="feature-description">inbox and notification</span> system featuring an
                                <span class="feature-description">anonymous hotline</span></li>
                            <li>An <span class="feature-description">announcement bulletin</span> where teachers can
                                post important announcements for all users to see
                            </li>
                            <li>A <span class="feature-description">preorder system</span> for Early College's No Left
                                Turn Cafe, which allows students to order online and receive status updates on their
                                orders
                            </li>
                            <li>A <span class="feature-description">project bulletin</span>, where teachers can post
                                unique and exceptional student projects from their classes
                            </li>
                            <li>Access to Alsion's online magazine, <span
                                        class="feature-description">Witherly Heights</span></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </article>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 block">
                <img class="image-block" src="https://i.imgur.com/j3Llf6r.jpg" alt="fancy pic">
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Block 3 -->
        <div class="row element" id="block-3">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <article class="text-block">
                    <div class="block-header red">
                        <h1 style="user-select: none; -moz-user-select: none;">Community</h1>
                    </div>
                    <div class="block-content mode">
                        <p>Saberchat reaches out to all members of Alsion's community - students, teachers and parents
                            in both Early College and Middle School.
                            As members of a small, tight-knit school, we value our community deeply. Saberchat will
                            strengthen the relationships between every member of the Alsion community.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </article>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 block">
                <img class="image-block" src="https://i.imgur.com/bDQsNAW.jpg" alt="fancy pic">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</main>
<%- include('./partials/footer') %>
<script>
    window.onload = (() => {
        window.onscroll = (() => {
            updateNav();
            animateDisplay();
        });
    });
</script>
</body>
</html>
